  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t成都大运会，大多数观众都是各机关单位组织参加，还有大量安保人员。普通人想去观赛十分困难。即便如此，还有各种安检和管控。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n像管监狱一样的开运动会，比1990年亚运会和2008年奥运会都糟的多。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n虽然也有洗地的，但是大家好像也都明白了<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDJmYmRkYjgzMDU2NzBiNDUwYTM4LnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTU5NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d2fbddb8305670b450a38.png?width=750&amp;height=595\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d2fbddb8305670b450a38.png?width=750&amp;height=595\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d2fbddb8305670b450a38.png?width=750&amp;height=595\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmNlZDJiYjRlZTBjMmIxZDc1ZWU1LmpwZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEwMDk\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fced2bb4ee0c2b1d75ee5.jpg?width=750&amp;height=1009\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fced2bb4ee0c2b1d75ee5.jpg?width=750&amp;height=1009\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fced2bb4ee0c2b1d75ee5.jpg?width=750&amp;height=1009\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzk0NGI2ODMwNjhjZTEwYjAxOTEyLnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEwMjI\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7944b683068ce10b01912.png?width=750&amp;height=1022\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7944b683068ce10b01912.png?width=750&amp;height=1022\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7944b683068ce10b01912.png?width=750&amp;height=1022\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTMzMTkyZTkwNWU3NzliZjhmNTI5LnBuZz93aWR0aD03NTAmaGVpZ2h0PTEyMjE\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/533192e905e779bf8f529.png?width=750&amp;height=1221\